text: Billy Unger (born October 15, 1995) is an American actor. He is best known for his role of Chase Davenport on the sitcom Lab Rats. Unger was born in southern Florida. When he was 11 years old, he moved to California for his acting career. ==References== Category:Actors from Florida Category:American television actors Category:1995 births Category:Living people
